<p><strong>The winners of the European Games Award 2012!</strong></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0.35cm; line-height: 115%;" class="western" lang="en-GB"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Congratulations to the best European Games, Studios, Publishers and Artists! And thanks a lot to all of our 230.000 voters from all over the world!! :-)</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0.35cm; line-height: 115%;" class="western" lang="en-GB"><img alt="1_ca03662" src="/images/stories/1_ca03662.jpg" height="412" width="620" /></p>
